amage came to the ruler. </div><div class="t mc8 x3e h24 y16a5 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m153c x5d h24 y1a6c ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">According to the testimony of his enemies, how faithful was </div><div class="t m1742 xbd h24 y17e1 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daniel? In what particular did they hope to find occasion against </div><div class="t m866 xbd h24 y22ec ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">him? Verses 4, 5. </div><div class="t m2455 x43 h24 yf65 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ </div><div class="t m1dfe x80 h33 yf65 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
